OL,3,CGovernment to launch new water
OL,4,Combudsman as trust in industry hits
OL,5,Cnew low
OL,7,FThe Government is set to announce
OL,8,Fstricter rules to protect customers as
OL,9,Fpublic trust in the water industry
OL,10,Freaches a new low.
OL,12,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed will
OL,13,Fpledge to create a new water ombudsman
OL,14,Fwith legal powers to resolve disputes,
OL,15,Freplacing the current voluntary system
OL,16,Fseen as too weak.
