OL,4,Combudsman as trust in industry hits
OL,5,Cnew low
OL,7,FThe changes, which will expand the
OL,8,Frole of the Consumer Council for Water
OL,9,F(CCW), will bring the sector into line
OL,10,Fwith other utilities by creating a
OL,11,Flegally binding consumer watchdog.
OL,13,FIt will also give customers a clear,
OL,14,Fsingle point of contact for
OL,15,Fcomplaints, ending confusion over
OL,16,Fwhere to turn.
