OL,7,FThe Department for the Environment,
OL,8,FFood and Rural Affairs said the new
OL,9,Fwatchdog would help "re-establish
OL,10,Fpartnership" between water companies
OL,11,Fand consumers.
OL,13,FIn May, a survey by the CCW found
OL,14,Ftrust in water companies had reached a
OL,15,Fnew low, with less than two-thirds of
OL,16,Fpeople saying they provided value for
OL,17,Fmoney.
