OL,7,FOnly 53% of people said they thought
OL,8,Fwater bills were fair, even before a
OL,9,F26% price hike came into force in
OL,10,FApril.
OL,12,FCCW chief executive Mike Keil welcomed
OL,13,Fthe move to create a mandatory
OL,14,Fombudsman, calling it a "key ask" for
OL,15,Fthe organisation to ensure people "can
OL,16,Fhave absolute confidence that when
OL,17,Fthey complain, they have robust
OL,18,Fprotection".
