OL,4,Combudsman as trust in industry hits
OL,5,Cnew low
OL,7,FThe new ombudsman is part of Mr Reed's
OL,8,Fbroader plans for a "root and branch
OL,9,Freform" of the water industry, to be
OL,10,Frevealed alongside a major review of
OL,11,Fthe sector on Monday.
OL,13,FFollowing publication of the review,
OL,14,Fhe is expected to say: "The water
OL,15,Findustry is broken. Our rivers, lakes
OL,16,Fand seas are polluted with record
OL,17,Flevels of sewage.
OL,19,F"Water pipes have been left to crumble
OL,20,Finto disrepair. Soaring water bills
OL,21,Fare straining family finances.
