OL,7,FThe key recommendation from the report
OL,8,Fis expected to involve scrapping Ofwat
OL,9,Fand creating a new regulator, which
OL,10,Fcould incorporate the work of the CCW.
OL,12,FShadow environment secretary Victoria
OL,13,FAtkins said stronger consumer
OL,14,Fprotections were "welcome in
OL,15,Fprinciple" but only "part of the
OL,16,Fserious long-term reforms the water
OL,17,Fsector needs".
