OL,7,FShe said: "We all want the water
OL,8,Fsystem to improve, and honesty about
OL,9,Fthe scale of the challenge is
OL,10,Fessential. Steve Reed must explain
OL,11,Fthat bill payers are paying for the
OL,12,F#104 billion investment plan.
OL,13,FMinisters must also explain how
OL,14,Freplacing one quango with another is
OL,15,Fgoing to clean up our rivers and lakes.
OL,17,F"Public confidence in the water system
OL,18,Fwill only be rebuilt through
OL,19,Ftransparency, resilience, and
OL,20,Fdelivery."
